metadata.description: An all-new series from the star of NBC's Parks & Recreation and veteran comic scribes DeFilippis and Weir! Ariana Von Holmberg is an heiress with a secret. But what she's hiding isn't a sex tape or a drug addiction or an affair with a professional golfer - it's a new career as a CIA operative! What better cover for an agent than a globe-trotting care-free femme with a penchant for flights of fancy? But can Ari balance her high society obligations with her new role as a spy or will the weight of two worlds bring her dual lives to a violent end?
metadata.name: Frenemy of the State, Vol. 1
